name: Restaurant World
overview: The most detailed, fun, and comprehensive restaurant site online. Restaurant patrons can search from close to a thousand different choices of items and experiences offered at restaurants throughout the United States of America. Patrons can review and exchange thoughts on every restaurant. Place your review about anything from the food taste and presentation , the seating comfort , down to the estimated wait for your check! Restaurant owners can list their name, address,and all of their detailed items offered on our ‘Advanced Search’ for free! Owners can also offer discounts for free as well! Premium memberships are available for only $125 a year. Owners can then add chef & owner profiles, photos, links, respond to reviews and much more! There is a lot to digest at Restaurant World! We hope you are hungry for the a true RESTAURANT ONLY website dedicated to the proud owners and happy customers!
